<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Hello Friend!</title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.2.0/css/bootstrap.min.css'>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Hello From Afar</h1>
    <p>Dear @Model.Recipient,</p>
    <p>How are you? I hope that you are having a nice weekend. I'm vacationing in @Model.Destination while I learn programming!</p>
    <p>@Model.Recipient, @Model.DestinationDesc</p>
    <p>But I like programming a lot, so I've got that going for me.</p>
    <p>Looking forward to seeing you soon. I'll bring you back @Model.Souvenir as a souvenir.</p>
    <p>Cheers,</p>
    <p>Travel Enthusiast @Model.Sender</p>
  </body>
</html>